{
  "stem": "24195.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The only thing that you could get in trouble with them, if you didn't do the work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the guards were all very-- I wouldn't say low class, but they were not a very intelligent group of people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were all-- I'm not trying to, you know, to make a-- a-- you know-- a discouraging statement about this department-- you know, downgrading construction people-- construction workers.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they were no match, really, for people like us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People that were in the camp, ranging from lawyers-- and even the German army officer who was in there, too, who had been recalled from the front and sent to the camp, because suddenly they decided that no longer can half Aryans be in the German army.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they were up until that point.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this guy was even, I think, he was a lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were all kinds of people-- doctors-- you know, all kinds of highly professional people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were no match for people that only built houses and break another building.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The other In charge-- that's what they are, construction people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With dogs, yeah, they had dogs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went out and got potatoes one morning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got back, and I-- I hid them in-- in my-- under my bunk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every night when I got-- somehow I got a pot, and I think-- and somehow I was able to make a fire and cook myself some potatoes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just eat-- that was supplementing the meager diet that we're getting in the normal-- that we get normally, with some potatoes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was a welcome addition, because we were so hungry.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
